      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW MATIC (4) was out of character last run when missing the frame, finishing eighth (30.61) in a Special conditions H at Sandown. Generally a safe beginner but buried in the ruck from a squeeze draw last time. Has won four of seven starts from this draw. Looks the one to beat on her best form. PAW WINKWORTH (1) goes very well at the course with two wins and a placing from four starts. Was out of placings last time (30.64) at The Meadows in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 3.5 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. PAW PALMER (5) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including four wins and two placings. Missed the frame latest (27.71) when fourth over 485m at this track in a SE. Looks a key chance on best figures. RIVERSDALE MICK (8) has strong credentials over this journey.",
